This rare Aqua Terra is fitted with a beautiful grey dial that is patterned with Teak Concept horizontal lines and equipped with a quick change date window. This 18K yellow gold spreads throughout the smooth plain bezel and crown, that are fixed to a 38.5mm stainless steel casebody and bracelet.
